Sydney CETNER, as Trustee of the Cetner Family Trust, petitioner,
v.
George A. CARTER and Songgin P. Carter, as Trustees of the Carter Family Trust dated March 1, 1991. No. 16-77. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 3, 2016.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeal of California, Second Appellate District denied.
